Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你還是離我而去時的那副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============op===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:55.63,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:11.28,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:21.75,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:33.83,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:44.42,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:50.58,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:56.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:00.80,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.14,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.15,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:55.63,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:11.28,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:21.75,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:33.83,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:44.42,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:50.58,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:56.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:00.80,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.14,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.15,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============op===============
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MI·XY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗西亞室有入侵者 艾麗西亞室有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標就一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封鎖通道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲大人 請退後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要退下的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在接到新的命令之前先在外面待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有翅膀的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到這麼快就和你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夏娃施加到Altair的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娃的詛咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣暫時就不會有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喉嚨還有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道阿馬塔同學他們是否平安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他答應過我不會亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答應…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與之交換 希望能你也能答應我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個世界裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從地面上幾乎看不到天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個奇怪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家才憧憬著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才對「Aquaria舞動於空」如此著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin也曾是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才好險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這裡也不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特到底在哪裡溜達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那個遊手好閒的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總算掌握了支配這個世界的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但話說回來 這些顶盖真是大煞风景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是削弱生命的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片大地跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在等候即將來臨的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此我可以感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所展现的力量的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及力量所彙聚的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把我關在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要進到裏面來 一切都好辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為找出不動總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來到了這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人十分引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而很容易就能找到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能為幫到大家的就只有這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這次不會再逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會找到總司令並帶他回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 修修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總算發現我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼總算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是拼命地四處找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在找我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是市場裏 還是在有軌電車裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或是在這個港口城市裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都一動不動地站在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體置於相互交錯的萬物中也決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的靈魂置於川流不息的時間中也決不挪移
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不挪移…不動搖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不為萬物所動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名為不動·ZEN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不動總司令從一萬二千年前開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正確來說是從二萬四千年前開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃·鈴白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想弄清一切真相嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經下定了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定不會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕真相有多麼殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要的就是這股氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候是殘酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距今12年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的Igler…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從Altair這顆星球上絕跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin·無雙是最後一個在Altair誕生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Igler已經絕跡的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能等著慢慢走向滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你們才會從我們的地球上掠走女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是需要一個能孕育出Altair的未來的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太恣意妄為了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能聽到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相還有後續
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且將更為殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 給我乖乖就範
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是前幾天被你們老大抓回來的大胸女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能開出比那黑亮的口子更大的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣放過你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的挖洞能力對生物根本不奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虜跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會找到你 然後將你擁入懷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來要到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃·鈴白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這個甜甜圈如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜甜圈在我手中靜止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但實際上卻以相同於船的速度在海上移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡海的甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得很不可思議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說穿了就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事物有時因為過於接近反而看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在應該在總司令腹中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否當真如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,構成甜甜圈的微粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縱使遭到分解也不會消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被攝入我體內之後可謂處於永遠靜止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從剛才開始就一味在進行著類似修禪問答的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有真相到底是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越一萬二千年的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續支撐著這星球大地的永恆的不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恆的不動尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就沉睡在這趟旅程的終點之上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到絲毫的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在X33區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去捉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲大人獨自留在艾麗西亞室裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自Vega的侵略者也在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娃的詛咒不僅讓我們星球上的Igler全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連從你們的世界帶來的眾多Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也同樣遭到了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們好不容易終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抵禦Altair的詛咒的稀有Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rare·Igler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連最強的Rare·Igler艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很遺憾地沒能勝任真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們憑什麼權利把媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是為了維繫Altair的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詛咒是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你們從地球上捉來的女性现在怎么樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷達以及紅外線傳感器皆無反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独重力波傳感器有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离90
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,80
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离0
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡 柚葉 你们还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而使用過力量的柚葉更令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是混账
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两人的身体到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到吗 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你脚下的塔内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你歸還的排場還真大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不是一起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像到了一个叫艾麗西亞室的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是被施加到Altair的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一開始也無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要亲眼目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都只能夠接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…SPADA的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是机械天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 快坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作要快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去婕希卡和柚葉的身体会支持不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一件事我非說不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您退後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那裡 開火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喚來了預備的Vector
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們坐到那上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚葉和婕希卡在上空待機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就拜託了 夥計們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚葉 你那措辭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那個了 專心對敵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,                    concerto
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有了女性那優美的 協奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就無法演奏禁斷的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調音合體 Go Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,                           Toccata
